data.description: ***SELLERS WILL ENTERTAIN OFFERS BETWEEN $399,000-$459,000. LIST PRICE EQUALS THE COMBINED UPPER AND LOWER VALUE RANGES.*** This home has SO MUCH to offer! Only 1 year old and in Like New condition PLUS the owner has installed a screened porch, a 6' privacy fence and a stand by generator making this a better deal than new construction! Energy efficient with tall ceilings, custom trim and cabinetry, quartz counter tops, a farmhouse sink, a custom built drop-zone and GE high end appliances. Gold Fortified Gold Construction! Beautiful LVP floors too! Stunning home with impressive fireplace and open kitchen with large center island. Floor plan is GREAT with a split/split arrangement - Primary Bedroom and Bath on one side, 2 Bedrooms with a Jack and Jill Bath on the other and 4th Bedroom is split from those with a private bath! Located in popular Grady Place in West Mobile Area.
